<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1055A" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW"><link href="text/shared/02/blockarrows.xhp">Block Arrows</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1056A" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW"><ahelp hid=".">Opens the Block Arrows toolbar from which you can insert graphics into your document.</ahelp></paragraph>
</section>
<section id="howtoget">
<embed href="text/shared/00/00000404.xhp#syblockarrows"/>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1059A" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Click an icon from the Block Arrows toolbar, then drag in the document to draw the shape.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="note" id="par_idN1059D" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Some shapes have a special handle which you can drag to change properties of the shape. The mouse pointer changes to a hand symbol over these special handles.</paragraph>
